      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car for a mechanic or for parts. The engine has a significant oil leak and struggles to maintain a consistent idle, often stalling at stoplights. The exterior shows its age with extensive rust along the wheel wells and several large dents, while the interior upholstery is heavily worn and in need of replacement. It is currently not reliable for daily use and will likely require a tow to its new destination.",
